s 20 indoor dog parks in Apex. Use the “Indoor Dog Park” filter on this page to jump straight to climate-controlled options.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Does Apex have a public dog park?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes, the Apex Nature Park and Hunter Street Dog Park are popular off-leash areas. Both require a pass for entry, ensuring a safe environment for vaccinated dogs.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Are there dog-friendly trails in Apex?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Absolutely. The Beaver Creek Greenway offers paved, scenic routes perfect for leashed walks. Salem Pond Park also provides a pleasant loop for a quick outing.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"What are the leash laws in Apex?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Apex maintains strict leash laws. Dogs must be on a leash and under the control of their owner when outside of their own property or designated off-leash areas.\\\"}}]}26:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$2e\\\"}}]\\n27:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"itemListElement\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Home\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":2,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type